Notes on web stuff:

1.  files in ~user/WWW  are visible.

2.  index.html is the default place the browser looks if pointed to a directory

3.  if there is no index.html then it provides a directory list, as for my
lecture notes.

4.  the default link for www.econ.uiuc.edu is the soft link index.html in 
/services/www/htdocs that points to ~roger/WWW/home.html  this file has
some broken gif links that should be fixed one fine day.

5.  the econ dept website is www.economics.uiuc.edu
